d Jitterbug which aims to be a bakery with a cafe feel complete with WiFi. To help fund this venture and to purchase some equipment, Jane put together a project on KickStarter.com to generate crowd sourced capital. The monetary goal was $15,000.00 and that was reached just 4  [&hellip;]\'>WPTavern: Congrats To Jane Wells</a></li></ul></div>', 'no'); 
